        "content": "<p>fitzgen opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12936\">PR #12936</a> from <code>fitzgen:array-new-elem-missing-stack-map</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>translate_array_new_elem</code> created a GC reference (array ref) via a libcall but<br>\ndid not call <code>builder.declare_value_needs_stack_map()</code> on the result. This meant<br>\nthe reference was not included in stack maps at subsequent safepoints, so if a<br>\nGC occurred, the reference became stale (leading to use-after-free within the GC<br>\nheap sandbox).</p>\n<p>Depends on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12935\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12935</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
